<h1>🏡 Monthly Property Care Tips</h1>

<p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>

<p>Here are this month's essential property maintenance tips to keep your
	{{#if isLandlord}}rental properties{{else}}home{{/if}}
	in excellent condition and prevent costly repairs.</p>

<h2>🗓️ {{formatDate currentDate 'MMMM YYYY'}} Maintenance Checklist</h2>

{{#if (eq month 'January')}}
	<div
		style='background: #e0f2fe; border-left: 4px solid #0288d1; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #01579b; margin-top: 0;'>❄️ Winter Preparation</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Check heating system:</strong>
				Replace filters, test thermostats</li>
			<li><strong>Prevent frozen pipes:</strong>
				Insulate exposed pipes, keep faucets dripping</li>
			<li><strong>Inspect weatherstripping:</strong>
				Seal gaps around doors and windows</li>
			<li><strong>Clear gutters:</strong> Remove ice dams and debris</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
{{else if (eq month 'February')}}
	<div
		style='background: #f3e8ff; border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #6b21a8; margin-top: 0;'>🔥 Indoor Comfort</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>HVAC maintenance:</strong>
				Check air filters and vents</li>
			<li><strong>Test smoke detectors:</strong>
				Replace batteries if needed</li>
			<li><strong>Inspect fireplaces:</strong>
				Clean chimneys, check dampers</li>
			<li><strong>Check for drafts:</strong>
				Add insulation where needed</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
{{else if (eq month 'March')}}
	<div
		style='background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #065f46; margin-top: 0;'>🌱 Spring Prep</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Exterior inspection:</strong>
				Check roof, siding, and foundation</li>
			<li><strong>Clean gutters:</strong>
				Clear debris and check for damage</li>
			<li><strong>Service air conditioning:</strong>
				Prepare for warmer weather</li>
			<li><strong>Inspect outdoor faucets:</strong>
				Check for winter freeze damage</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
{{else if (eq month 'April')}}
	<div
		style='background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #92400e; margin-top: 0;'>🌸 Spring Maintenance</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Deep clean:</strong>
				Windows, screens, and outdoor spaces</li>
			<li><strong>Landscaping prep:</strong>
				Trim trees, plant flowers, fertilize lawn</li>
			<li><strong>Check deck/patio:</strong>
				Inspect for winter damage, clean and seal</li>
			<li><strong>Test outdoor lighting:</strong>
				Replace bulbs, check timers</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
{{else if (eq month 'May')}}
	<div
		style='background: #ecfdf5; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #065f46; margin-top: 0;'>🏡 Exterior Focus</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Power washing:</strong>
				Clean siding, walkways, and driveways</li>
			<li><strong>Inspect irrigation:</strong>
				Test sprinkler systems and timers</li>
			<li><strong>Paint touch-ups:</strong>
				Address any exterior paint chips</li>
			<li><strong>Check caulking:</strong> Reseal windows and doors</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
{{else}}
	<div
		style='background: #e0f2fe; border-left: 4px solid #0288d1; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;'
	>
		<h3 style='color: #01579b; margin-top: 0;'>🔧 General Maintenance</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>HVAC check:</strong> Change filters, clean vents</li>
			<li><strong>Plumbing inspection:</strong>
				Check for leaks, test water pressure</li>
			<li><strong>Safety check:</strong>
				Test smoke/carbon monoxide detectors</li>
			<li><strong>Exterior walkthrough:</strong>
				Look for any damage or wear</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
{{/if}}

<h2>⚡ Priority Action Items</h2>

<div
	style='background: #fee2e2; border: 1px solid #f87171; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;'
>
	<h3 style='color: #dc2626; margin-top: 0;'>🚨 Address Immediately</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Water leaks or moisture issues</li>
		<li>Electrical problems or exposed wiring</li>
		<li>HVAC system failures</li>
