			<li><strong>Preventive maintenance:</strong>
				Small fixes now prevent big repairs later</li>
			<li><strong>Seasonal inspections:</strong>
				Catch issues before they become costly</li>
			<li><strong>Quality materials:</strong>
				Invest in durable fixtures and appliances</li>
			<li><strong>Professional relationships:</strong>
				Build relationships with reliable contractors</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

